*The Library Management System (LMS) is a Java-based application designed to efficiently manage library operations.*

*Features*
User Management: Used by User, Admin, Super_Admin.
Transaction    : ViewBook, IssueBook, ReturnBook , ChangePassword, SubmitFeedback , Logout, addbook, viewuser, deleteuser,
                 deleteAdmin, viewFeedback, viewIssuedBooks, search Book
Main method    : Register -> Login -> verifyDetails-> Display Menu

*Technology Stack*
Backend : Java (JDBC for database connectivity)
Database: MySQL
Development Tools: Eclipse/IntelliJ, MySQL Workbench

*Connection DBMS*
JAR Files
